Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現大量歐洛斯型
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(700,655)}Eurus
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\an7}註：歐洛斯 希臘神話中的東風風神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們不是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的內核覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我們更快趕到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迅速擊退敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍宮島部隊負責救助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美三香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這種地方嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凍住對手然後同化嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅳ…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲洋！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會保護大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:26.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見…前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:32.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暉！聽得到嗎？暉！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:42.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍宮島…來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 同步連接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暉！大家在哪裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見前輩…被敵人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請…快去救她…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:05:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捕獲D島的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海因茨和一部輔助機被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,申請發射「暴君」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(720,655)}tyrant
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遠見！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想全部燒光嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這也算人嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人產生的火啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火燒的感覺我不喜歡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類軍真是卑鄙透頂！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一顆也不許讓它掉下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回島上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎 住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎——!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了 你是我送去的臥底
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否定的話會被幹掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多拿點毯子來！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救護班 這邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登記完畢的請到裡面來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活著回來了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還好你沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 都是多虧了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先回來的那些人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:17.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧爾嘉的傷好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們…都被敵人幹掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…媽的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溝口先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿廣…呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:32.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內核順利到達了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾梅莉 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去做個檢查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先替大家檢查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弓子！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鶴媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然看過報告 不過還是沒想到居然長到了這麼大…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上檢查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是開著法芙娜回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸會 美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有艾梅莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會說人類的語言嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這樣更能理解你們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來主操 和之前存在過的那個一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 我救了你們了 可以把你同化了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美羽？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對他做了這種保證？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高興能得到你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要等全世界的人都和平了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰也不再悲傷和疼痛了才可以把我吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你就幫我們到那個時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 我也可以提個要求嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼要求？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我套衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:10:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認到5001名生還
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珀耳修斯中隊九成人員陣亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真虧他們能撐到這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機庫報告 已收納Mk.Nicht及Mk.Ⅹ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Sein也已回收
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Sein居然…變成了這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面有生命反應
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓緊時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:31.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這同化現象真夠嚴重的 一般人根本就動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是有救兵來就危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是請御門先生做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我改名叫近藤咲良了 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚禮辦了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在神社辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也希望大家都在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到廣登和遠見被抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人類軍…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 追不上他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:05.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是有辦法和他們談判的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.45,0:12:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我想聊聊機體的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡農在機庫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡農她…不在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:22.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已經…不在…任何地方了 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個果然是美三香嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點點…殘存的心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都變成這樣了還…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真了不起 美三香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是末期症狀差點就發作了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是幹了多亂來的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於你派出了自己的孩子之事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:13:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是用一百萬個感謝和道歉也不足以表達心意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這孩子像他媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己所相信的道路就想走到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到頭來 我也只能送他上路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還有辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是Mir的因子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒必要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島會祝福一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mir的祝福？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會說人類的語言…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能讓你的Mir在島上安家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為Mir會互相同化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有另外一個讓他紮根的新天地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:49.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被新聯合國葬送的島嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三Alvis
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(Partb)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:59.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在與虛無的邊界…這是島的祝福嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所憎恨的Mk.Nicht是只屬於你的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是為希望而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能捨棄他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是談判需要他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要救真矢 還是救世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都救
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會讓島的內核失望的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我的名字 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.55,0:14:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,織姬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請允許我出島
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在接受祝福之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的生命似乎還不會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便消失了 你的生命也一定會持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是指…由Mir主導的死亡和再生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的Mir在另一個島上紮根的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和你的容器就會重生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能看到這樣的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未來…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來其實不應該告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你應該能不懼未來 到達那裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想像普通的親人那樣生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就祈求這樣的未來能夠實現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為我們曾經存在的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士前輩 歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 沒能把他帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:46.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到希望了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 他活到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.80,0:15:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能救出廣登和遠見前輩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會把他們帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:15:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 沒想到是個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老實點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光弘？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛在哪！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快給我走！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別碰我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說他是新聯合國的間諜有點奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和被敵人同化的傢伙待在一塊 所以變得不正常了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:55.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,間諜？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.82,0:16:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我說你 給我換上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:16:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你沒事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣 比利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是哥哥 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在這兒換 趕緊的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我斃了你！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}別磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓他們住手吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女孩打下了轟炸機
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在沒殺了她已經算她走運了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.53,0:17:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,D島的人移植了敵人的因子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 你什麼時候會閃金光啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光弘·巴特藍的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然冷靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是新聯合國秘書長赫絲特·蓋洛普
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(822,655)}Hester Gallop
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一件事需要你協助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我去開法芙娜是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悟性不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為過去我父親就是這樣希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救世主型 Mk.Raison
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\an7}註：法語中「理由」「理性」之意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你做它的測試駕駛員 我就不向你問罪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,——害死誠實勇敢的人類軍士兵的罪過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…我那個開Mk.Ⅴ的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說他的遺體被回收了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:05.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們殺了他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說他是在戰鬥中喪命的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們對光弘做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光弘？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你說傀儡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傀儡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有權知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普羅米修斯的岩窟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(578,655)}Prometheus
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有極少數人能進入的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的聖域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過去在日本發現的瀨戶內海Mir被分為三份
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由三個Alvis管理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這曾經是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是第三Alvis——亞特蘭提斯的內核
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(762,655)}Atlantis
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\an7}註：傳說中的巨型島嶼 後來被洪水毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Alvis…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 牠也是其他個體的內核
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿撒謝爾型流浪者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(744,655)}Vagrant
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在天堂之門作戰中得到的Mir變異體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全世界唯一一個空間站
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能進行衛星通訊和誘敵的 都只有我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.34,0:20:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外 巴特藍的研究也產生了各種各樣的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傀儡也是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光弘…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂傀儡 就是這個內核的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:21:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們以各種姿態出生 給流浪者帶去情報
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是能夠自如操縱的便利的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是巴特藍製造的傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.74,0:21:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你向我們洩露情報 奪去了那雷恩的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽你們的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你們了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是慈悲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果強行操縱傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其人格總有一天會崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是要將他從這份痛苦中解救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑…！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.81,0:21:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是光弘·巴特藍的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人類軍的士兵！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通告普羅米修斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消除傀儡MB-7型的人格
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.04,0:22:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心…要消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.34,0:22:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要讓你知道很多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好讓你繼承你父親的遺志
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面命令你從今往後在這裡生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.16,0:22:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請讓我回到之前的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果反抗 你就會被洗腦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.42,0:22:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖聽話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.71,0:22:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了回到同伴身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.13,0:22:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要放棄希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.36,0:23:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是…什麼地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.45,0:23:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在等待和你融為一體的這一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們製造又消滅了許多的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.79,0:23:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也殺光了我原來所在的島上所有的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是每當有人死去 力量就變得更強
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 你這個容器誕生了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.01,0:23:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們所有人的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.22,0:23:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憎恨的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.62,0:24:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是…憎恨！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是…！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,（ED）
